Localization.Name: Smoltz (Bottle)
Localization.Description:
HEI: 18
Effects: Cognitive Impairment, Dehydrating

Crafted from select rice and barley for a traditional flavor passed down by generations of brewmasters. That’s the taste of Smoltz.
